org.fosstrak.epcis.repository.query
Class QueryOperationsWebService

java.lang.Object
  org.fosstrak.epcis.repository.query.QueryOperationsWebService
All Implemented Interfaces:
EPCISServicePortType
public class QueryOperationsWebService
extends Object
implements EPCISServicePortType

This class redirects the calls received from the Web service stack to the underlying QueryOperationsModule and ensures that any uncaught exception is properly catched and wrapped into an ImplementationExceptionResponse.

Author:
Marco Steybe
